data.description:
INSTANT EQUITY!!! BACK ON THE MARKET!! At no fault of it's own! AND seller is offering 3k in concessions towards closing cots or buy downs!!! Title work is done! 
This gorgeous home sits on just over 2 acres (MOL) on the outskirts of town in the gated, established community of Four Lakes. Double doors upon entrance, built-ins throughout the home, granite countertops in the bathroom and kitchen, large walk-in pantry and SO MUCH STORAGE! GIGANTIC, fenced in backyard with generous sized covered patio, perfect for entertaining or relaxing. The primary suite has sitting space, access to the backyard, an oversized bathroom with jetted tub and separate shower and large closet! The garage is large with a mini split a/c and a storm shelter! Neighborhood ponds to fish!! Plenty of space between neighbors!!  Bring your buyers to see this home! PICS COMING SOON! Buyer to verify all information!
